{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"长生不老的僮仆，轮流着服待他们，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"捧着盏和壶，与满杯的醴泉；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"他们不因那醴泉而头痛，也不酩酊。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他们有自己所选择的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"和自己所爱好的鸟肉。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"还有白皙的、美目的妻子，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"好像藏在蚌壳里的珍珠一样。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"那是为了报酬他们的善行。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他们在乐园里，听不到恶言和谎话，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"但听到说：祝你们平安！祝你们平安！"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"幸福者，幸福者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他们享受无刺的酸枣树，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"结实累累的（香蕉）树；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"漫漫的树荫；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"泛泛的流水；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"丰富的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"四时不绝，可以随意摘食；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"与被升起的床榻。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"我使她们重新生长，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"我使她们常为处女，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"依恋丈夫，彼此同岁；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"这些都是幸福者所享受的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"许多前人"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"和许多后人。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"薄命者，薄命者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"他们在毒风和沸水中，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"在黑烟的阴影下，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"既不凉爽，又不美观。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"以前他们确是奢侈的，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"确是固执大罪的，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"他们常说：“难道我们死后，已变成尘土和枯骨的时候，我们必定要复活吗？ ”"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"连我们的祖先，也要复活吗？”"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"你说：前人和后人，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"在一个著名的日期和特定时间必定要被集合。"}]}